modules.description: This module implements delimited continuation operators using the `Delimcc_of_fxhandler` library, enabling advanced control flow manipulations. It provides functions like `new_prompt`, `push_prompt`, `take_subcont`, and `push_subcont` to manage prompts and subcontinuations, along with `shift`, `control`, `shift0`, `control0`, and `abort` for capturing and invoking delimited continuations. These operations are useful for implementing non-local transfers of control, backtracking, coroutines, and exception-like mechanisms with precise control over stack manipulation.
